                     <interp inst="t18190915-151-person1363" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I am a watchman. On the 29th of August, about two o'clock in the morning, I heard something fall, saw the prisoner going down the lane, and secured him with the lamb in his apron.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18190915-151-person1364">
                  RICHARD 
                  COATES
               <interp inst="t18190915-151-person1364" type="surname" value="COATES"></interp>
