                     <interp inst="t18190915-151-person1364" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . The prisoner was given into my charge. I found several hooks on him, and lines to put down areas; I also found a rod on him.</p>
               <p>Prisoner's Defence. I was distressed.</p>
